- @weimar_coalition_hansa
- @grand_coalition_hansa
- @bourgeois_coalition_hansa
- @right_coalition_hansa
- @no_majority_hansa




@united_left_coalition_hansa
title: The <span style="color: #E3000F;">Social Democrats</span> form a coalition with the <span style="color: #8B0000;">**KPD**</span>!
subtitle: <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: #8B0000;">**KPD**</span> ([+ united_left_coalition_hansa +]%)
view-if: united_left_coalition_hansa > 50
on-arrival: in_united_left_coalition_hansa = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@weimar_coalition_hansa
title: A Weimar Coalition can be formed.
subtitle: <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> ([+ weimar_coalition_hansa +]%)
view-if: weimar_coalition_hansa > 50
on-arrival: in_weimar_coalition_hansa = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@grand_coalition_hansa
title: We can form a Grand Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> ([+ grand_coalition_hansa +]%)
view-if: grand_coalition_hansa > 50
on-arrival: in_grand_coalition_hansa = 1; nlp_hansa = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@bourgeois_coalition_hansa
title: We can form a Bourgeois Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span>[? if not rdp_formed: + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span> ?][? if wp_exist: + <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> ?][? if csvd_exist: + <span style="color: #1DB4E1;">**CSVD**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> ([+ bourgeois_coalition_hansa +]%)
view-if: bourgeois_coalition_hansa > 50
on-arrival: in_bourgeois_coalition_hansa = 1; nlp_hansa = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@right_coalition_hansa
title: We can form a Right Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span> [? if kvp_exist: + <span style="color: #455B95;">**KVP**</span> ?][? if kswr_exist: + <span style="color: #003755;">**KSWR**</span> ?][? if wp_exist: + <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span> ?][? if csvd_exist: + <span style="color: #1DB4E1;">**CSVD**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> ([+ right_coalition_hansa +]%)
view-if: right_coalition_hansa > 50
on-arrival: in_right_coalition_hansa = 1; nlp_hansa = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@no_majority_hansa
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: united_left_coalition_hansa <= 50 and weimar_coalition_hansa <= 50 and grand_coalition_hansa <= 50 and bourgeois_coalition_hansa <= 50 and right_coalition_hansa <= 50 and nlp_hl <= 50
on-arrival: nlp_hansa = 1 if was_nlp_hansa; in_nlp_majority_hansa = 1 if was_in_nlp_majority_hansa; in_united_left_coalition_hansa = 1 if was_in_united_left_coalition_hansa; in_weimar_coalition_hansa = 1 if was_in_weimar_coalition_hansa; in_grand_coalition_hansa = 1 if was_in_grand_coalition_hansa; in_bourgeois_coalition_hansa = 1 if was_in_bourgeois_coalition_hansa; in_right_coalition_hansa = 1 if was_in_right_coalition_hansa;

There is no path to a majority government for now. The current government will stay in power as a minority coalition.





